Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:18.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:24.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:30.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:37.14,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:42.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:53.19,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:58.40,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:01.53,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:06.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:13.17,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,that blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:18.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:24.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:36.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been almost a year since the\NMacross began its voyage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and we have amassed a sizable amount\Nof valuable data.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:40.19,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(74,132)}GLOBAL REPORT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:43.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now report all we've learned\Nto the UN Forces High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:48.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From the space battleship\NSDF-1 Macross, UN Forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,this is Captain Bruno J. Global.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For those on Earth, I think it's hard\Nto know just what befell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:02.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the Macross and its surroundings on\Nthe day of the launch ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and what happened once it and\Nthe island both disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:10.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It all began with a sudden roar\Nfrom the Macross's main gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,W...What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:14.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:17.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The ship's original systems have\Njust activated themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:18.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:20.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!\NIt's entered firing mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The main cannon is activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:07.94,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently engaged in\Nhostilities with alien forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.80,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:12.14,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, this is not a drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:23.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The directive from the previous day's defense\Ncouncil that we were not to fire first
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,in the event of an alien encounter had\Nbeen thoroughly broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From what we could gather of the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:34.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the alien's enemies had left the Macross\Nbehind as a clever trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,a booby trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of our battle with\Nthe enemy's land forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:35.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we confirmed that they were giants, five or\Nsix times the size of human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:41.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This matches earlier estimates made\Nby UN Forces High Command
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:44.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,based on the size of\Nthe interior of the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:05:00.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We also gained valuable data on the\Neffectiveness of the Battroids,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,which had been designed to combat\Nsuch a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:09.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, we attempted to launch the ship\Nusing the gravity control system...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but we failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!\NThe bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They appear to be the gravity control systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The gravity control systems?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:51.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An analysis by our technical crew concluded\Nthat the unexpected firing of the main gun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:56.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,had affected all of the ship's components,\Nincluding the Fold System.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:06:00.29,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After transporting the Macross and\Nthe nearby island to Pluto's orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:05.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the Fold System vanished, forcing us\Nto make a long voyage home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We quickly docked the Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,with the aircraft carrier Prometheus\Nand the assault ship Daedalus,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:57.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,then brought the base and various\Nfacilities from the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:02.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as 50,000-plus refugees we found in the\Nshelters, into the ship itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:08.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The civilians used materials from\Nthe island to rebuild their city
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:12.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,inside the ship's residential areas\Nand went about their daily lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:17.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this will provide valuable data\Nfor future deep-space voyages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,On a related note, we learned that the\Ndisappearance of the Fold System
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,cut the energy lines to the main gun,\Nrendering it unusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:29.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, the ship had to undergo\Na Transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:33.06,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie squadrons, all units, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:38.13,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, Valkyrie squadrons,\Nall units, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:10.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to initiate\Nthe ship-wide Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:36.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret that the Transformation affected\Nthe citizens so badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:40.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but it allowed us to strike back at our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Following that, we were able\Nto modify the process
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:46.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,to minimize the damage caused\Nby future Transformations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:51.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, for our first counterattack\Nin the rings of Saturn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:56.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we used residual energy from the Fold System\Nto create the Pinpoint Barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:10:00.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, by concentrating the Barrier\Nat the bow of the Daedalus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:04.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we developed the Daedalus Attack, which has\Nproven effective against the giant enemy ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!\NI'll never make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Agh, not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:14.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, I am hastening development of a\Nbarrier that can cover the entire ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the eighth month of our voyage,\Nin need of supplies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:35.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we touched down at Mars Base Salla,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:38.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,where we were trapped by hidden gravity mines\Nthat had been planted by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:08.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroid groups 6, 8, and 17\Nare destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:09.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest are heavily damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. We may be able to disable\Nthat trap after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how, if it's underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:19.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The reactor! Salla's reactor is located\Ndeep beneath the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can blow it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, begin the operation at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:34.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have Hayase activate the reactor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reactor is overloading!\NDanger! Danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:02.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Safety systems are disengaged. Status red!\NReactor entering critical cascade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen minutes until detonation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All personnel, evacuate!\NAll personnel, evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:10.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,By causing the reactor located\Nbeneath the base to overload,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Hayase enabled us to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:41.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's objective seems to be the capture of\Nour ship rather than its destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:48.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe this is what allowed the Macross to run\Nfor so long from an overwhelming enemy force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate the launch of MBS,\Nthe Macross Broadcast System,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we present the Miss Macross Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ship-wide civilian broadcasts began,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Miss Macross contest was\Nheld to mark the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will make it to the finals\Nand win the crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss Macross Contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:11.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our queen will be chosen by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:17.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A young girl named Lynn Minmay\Nwas crowned Miss Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:23.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Earth in sight, a fleet of enemy ships\Nsurrounded us, forcing us to a stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:29.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was at this time that the enemy\Nsubtly changed its tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:44.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The jamming that had blocked\Nour communications ceased,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:48.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and we immediately reported our\Nsituation to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:50.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However, directly following this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:54.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a signal from someplace\Nthat isn't High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on the speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:58.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:05.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...name of the Zentradi, we order you\Nto surrender your vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The recent attack was merely a show of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:11.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If... do not wish to be destroyed,\Nyou will surrender immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from the enemy fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...receive this demand for surrender...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:24.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's deciphering abilities\Nare exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We mustn't be careless with\Nour communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When our radar was destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:44.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Misa Hayase went out on a\Nrecon patrol in a Cat's Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:31.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Hayase, along with 2nd Lt. Ichijo\Nand Corporals Kakizaki and Jenius,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:38.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,were captured and taken all the way to the\Nmain Zentradi base for questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:46.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, they miraculously escaped and\Nwere able to tell us the shocking truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:50.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let them explain it in their own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:03.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Bodolzaa, Supreme Commander of\Nthe Zentradi 118th main fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some things I wish to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They know our language!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:13.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,My Lord, the translation device appears\Nto be working properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. When did you people make contact\Nwith the Supervision Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Supervision Army"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You ever heard of that army, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:23.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just joined the military myself,\Nso I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just joined the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world did you do before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? We were civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ci-vil-ians"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:34.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,, What does "civilian" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who doesn't fight in wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:38.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't fight in wars?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:39.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,P... Preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:44.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The universe overflows with conflict, and\Nit is in battle that one finds life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's in battle that one finds life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:51.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,, It seems that we need to change\Nour line of questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:55.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there really people aboard\Nyour ship who do not fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:57.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And how can your men and\Nwomen live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:01.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Men and women together? What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:01.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Kakizaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to answer any\Nmore questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be their commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:18.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,None of you appreciate the\Nsituation you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:25.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have enough power to destroy your\Nship and your world in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at that planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:01.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want the same thing to\Nhappen to your homeworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:09.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something's strange. They have\Nthat kind of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:13.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so why haven't they launched an all-out\Nattack on the Macross and the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:17.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will ask you once more:\NDo these "civilians" really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:21.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And how can men and women\Ncoexist on the same ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Civilians... Men and women...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:27.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe we have something that they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:31.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't answer, I'll destroy\Nyour ship and your planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really think you can,\Nthen go ahead and try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:43.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have powers you know nothing about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:44.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:49.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:53.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:57.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:20:00.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that fragile miclones\Nlike this dare to defy us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, why did you go through the\Ntrouble of becoming a miclone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:09.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell me why you became\Na miclone, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:13.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:16.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were born with these bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Born with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And just where were you "born" from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From our mothers, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mothers"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our female parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you were born from a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How? You don't even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:37.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A man and a woman make love,\Nand together they make a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:40.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Make love"? How is this done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they kiss and hold each other, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is how miclones are "born"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:48.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,, You two, show me this "kissing."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:52.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break! Two guys\Ncan't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, then I'll crush you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:55.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You? Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:09.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Ichijo, kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our chance to see\Nhow the enemy reacts!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do it with Kakizaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:21.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you can't just say something like that and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:25.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Protoculture...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Protoculture"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:57.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Take these things\Naway immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:22:00.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What could the Zentradi have feared so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:07.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their giant bodies are so strong that they\Ncan survive for short periods in the vacuum of space,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:13.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and they have an unbelievably powerful\Nfleet as well. All that strength and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:16.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.10,0:22:21.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:23.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. You're very considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:24.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this late already, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:39.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:46.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd see this sight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:49.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:52.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange to say now, but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:56.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bad feeling when\NI was given this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:22:59.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A feeling that by launching the Macross,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:01.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,something would happen that\Nwould change our...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:04.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that would change humanity forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your premonition came true\Nin a way, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:11.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What will the Macross mean for us in the end?
