Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:23.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.16,0:24:29.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.25,0:24:36.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.58,0:24:44.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.14,0:24:50.51,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.64,0:24:56.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.17,0:25:04.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.68,0:25:15.92,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, The light that shines so far away
